<item>
            <title>[SPR-1102] Problem with PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer since refactoring of PropertyResourceConfigurer</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-1102</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Previously in the PropertyResourceConfigurer &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  InputStream is = location.getInputStream();&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;was insde the try/catch block.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now it is outside the try/catch block in PropertiesLoaderSupport which is causing FileNotFoundException when using a config like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;propertyConfigurer&quot; class=&quot;org.springframework.beans.factory.config.PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;ignoreUnresolvablePlaceholders&quot; value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;ignoreResourceNotFound&quot; value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;locations&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;list&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;!-- This is used when in application mode --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;/my.properties&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;!-- This is used when in web-application mode --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;/WEB-INF/my.properties&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/list&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
