                            <comment id="13751" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Tue, 5 Jul 2005 11:48:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report - that unfortunately slipped in due to the factoring out of the PropertiesLoaderSupport base class. I&apos;ve fixed this in CVS already; please give the next nightly snapshot a try to see whether it works for you again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13752" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Tue, 5 Jul 2005 11:55:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve also added a corresponding unit test: &quot;ignoreResourceNotFound&quot; didn&apos;t have a proper unit test before; that&apos;s why it could slip through.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
